desc: At Dhiman's Kebab and Pizza, we serve a delicious fusion of mouth-watering kebabs and delicious pizzas, made with the finest ingredients and bold flavors. Whether you're a fan of sizzling kebabs or freshly baked cheesy pizzas, every bite promises an unforgettable experience. Discover the best kebabs and pizzas in the city – a must-see for food lovers in Portugal! Our passion for quality food and exceptional service ensures that every visit is a delight. Come and enjoy the perfect combination of flavor, tradition and innovation at Dhiman's Kebab and Pizza! For orders or comments, please do not hesitate to contact us at +351 920 097 401 or visit us at R.do Rosmaninho Lote 5 esq, 2135-083 Samora Correia, Portugal. We are always happy to assist you!
